message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as it deals with speech and audio processing. Other likely categories could be cs.CL (computational linguistics) as the paper deals with speech synthesis and voice conversion, cs.LG (machine learning) as the paper uses deep residual neural networks, cs.CR (cryptography and security) as the paper deals with spoofing attacks, and cs.CV (computer vision and pattern recognition) as the paper deals with feature representations.
